---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy | MyGreekTax"
  description="Information about how MyGreekTax uses cookies."
  canonicalPath="/cookies/"
>
  <main style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 1.5rem;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;color:#28251d;">
    <a href="/" style="font-size:0.875rem;color:#C9923A;text-decoration:none;">← Back to MyGreekTax</a>
    <h1 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.5rem;margin:1.5rem 0 0.5rem;">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:#7a7974;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Last updated: 1 July 2026</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">Our Approach</h2>
    <p><strong>We do not use tracking cookies or advertising cookies.</strong></p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">Analytics</h2>
    <p>We use <strong>Plausible Analytics</strong> — no cookies, no personal data, fully GDPR/CCPA/PECR compliant.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">Google Fonts</h2>
    <p>Fonts are loaded from Google's CDN. Your IP may be logged by Google. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#C9923A;">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">No Consent Banner Required</h2>
    <p>Because we do not use cookies requiring consent under GDPR/PECR, we do not display a cookie consent banner.</p>
    <h2 style="font-size:1.25rem;margin:2rem 0 0.5rem;">Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@mygreektax.eu" style="color:#C9923A;">hello@mygreektax.eu</a></p>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
